01:32:20.916 --> 01:32:22.317
Okay, I forgive you.

01:32:22.791 --> 01:32:24.666
Thanks, Yah.

01:32:24.750 --> 01:32:27.000
And I want to ask for your help.

01:32:27.041 --> 01:32:28.375
Just one thing.

01:32:29.375 --> 01:32:30.791
Rio, come here.

01:32:34.291 --> 01:32:35.000
Yah...

01:32:35.916 --> 01:32:38.791
...please bring my son on stage.

01:32:39.839 --> 01:32:40.519
What?

01:32:41.166 --> 01:32:43.000
I promised him...

01:32:43.375 --> 01:32:46.000
...that I would bring him with me on stage.

01:32:46.541 --> 01:32:49.042
But because I'm not going to perform...

01:32:49.916 --> 01:32:52.416
...I can't keep my promise.

01:32:56.291 --> 01:32:58.416
I'm not a great parent.

01:32:59.750 --> 01:33:01.125
Far from it.

01:33:02.916 --> 01:33:05.291
That's why I'm asking for your help.

01:33:06.914 --> 01:33:09.333
Please bring him on stage with you, Yah...

01:33:10.916 --> 01:33:13.416
...so he won't be disappointed at me.

01:33:15.041 --> 01:33:17.916
He really wants to watch the performance
from the stage.

01:33:25.125 --> 01:33:26.750
Help me.

01:33:33.625 --> 01:33:35.916
Let's call...

01:33:37.791 --> 01:33:40.541
...Yayahh Aduduh!

01:33:40.625 --> 01:33:42.666
Yayah!

01:33:42.791 --> 01:33:50.541
Yayah!

01:34:07.666 --> 01:34:11.416
Good evening, Larung Pes.

01:34:11.541 --> 01:34:14.125
Let me hear it, Larung Pes!

01:34:16.789 --> 01:34:18.292
Really like the spirit.

01:34:19.416 --> 01:34:21.416
Guys...

01:34:21.541 --> 01:34:23.291
Come sing with me!

01:35:39.291 --> 01:35:40.625
Don't step on the cable.

01:35:40.666 --> 01:35:45.000
Who wants a surprise?

01:35:45.041 --> 01:35:50.000
Give it up for Tata Ria Buana!

01:35:52.166 --> 01:35:55.666
Tata!

01:35:57.416 --> 01:35:58.666
Rio!

01:35:59.791 --> 01:36:01.125
Music!

01:36:33.375 --> 01:36:35.041
Rio!

01:36:35.087 --> 01:36:37.337
I'm performing at Larung Pes!

01:36:37.500 --> 01:36:38.750
Come here!

01:37:07.875 --> 01:37:09.875
Let's go home to Jakarta.

01:38:06.875 --> 01:38:08.750
Dad doesn't recognize us anymore.

01:38:12.666 --> 01:38:13.792
Yes.

01:38:26.291 --> 01:38:28.500
I want to apologize to him.

01:38:34.916 --> 01:38:36.333
I can't, can I?

01:38:41.041 --> 01:38:43.041
It's okay. Let's just go home.

01:38:55.392 --> 01:38:56.209
Naya.

01:38:58.541 --> 01:38:59.875
I have an idea.

01:39:12.875 --> 01:39:15.166
Thank you!

01:39:19.125 --> 01:39:21.416
Thank you, Yayah!

01:39:21.441 --> 01:39:22.650
Congrats'!

01:39:24.416 --> 01:39:25.666
You can do it.

01:41:28.916 --> 01:41:30.166
Dad?

01:41:31.375 --> 01:41:32.916
Dad, do you remember me?

01:41:34.041 --> 01:41:35.666
Yes.

01:41:35.791 --> 01:41:37.791
Lauralei.

01:41:37.875 --> 01:41:40.041
My beautiful youngest daughter.

01:41:58.291 --> 01:41:59.416
Hold this.

01:42:02.625 --> 01:42:05.042
Dad. It's Naya here.

01:42:15.166 --> 01:42:18.041
Dad. I'm Naya. Do you remember me?

01:42:18.125 --> 01:42:19.666
Naya.

01:42:19.791 --> 01:42:21.083
Yes.

01:42:22.125 --> 01:42:24.000
Naya!

01:42:34.166 --> 01:42:37.000
Dad, I'm sorry.

01:42:38.916 --> 01:42:40.625
I love you.

01:43:12.125 --> 01:43:18.250
SIX MONTHS LATER

01:43:29.500 --> 01:43:32.458
Nurse, where are you taking me?

01:43:32.689 --> 01:43:34.625
Do you forget?

01:43:34.845 --> 01:43:38.792
Every Saturday,
there's a musical performance at the park.

01:43:40.579 --> 01:43:41.375
Yes.

01:44:12.166 --> 01:44:14.667
What's the name of the singer?

01:44:15.125 --> 01:44:16.666
Nayara...

01:44:16.791 --> 01:44:17.916
...Amalia...

01:44:18.041 --> 01:44:19.166
...Wardhani.

01:44:19.291 --> 01:44:20.500
Naya.

01:44:21.666 --> 01:44:23.541
Such a beautiful name.

01:45:36.642 --> 01:45:38.767
Be patient, Wan. Five more minutes.

01:45:40.166 --> 01:45:41.416
We have a lot of stuff here.

01:45:41.500 --> 01:45:44.000
Where's your curly-haired friend
who often helps us carrying our stuff?

01:45:44.163 --> 01:45:46.579
My friend? He's your friend!

01:45:46.750 --> 01:45:48.708
You're kidding.

01:45:49.291 --> 01:45:51.000
So, whose friend is that? Yours?

01:45:51.633 --> 01:45:52.500
What?

01:45:52.666 --> 01:45:53.750
I don't know.

01:45:54.041 --> 01:45:55.500
He's not your friends?

01:46:04.916 --> 01:46:06.291
So, who is he?

01:46:06.375 --> 01:46:07.833
Wait, who am I?
